  "history": "",
  "relationship": "Two people have just met and are still unfamiliar with each other. Their conversations are mostly polite and superficial, limited to everyday topics like work, studies, or the weather. At this stage, both sides are cautious and have yet to reveal their true selves.",
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "已到工位 \n你可以开始和我聊原生家庭的破碎，情人的隔阂，伴侣的争吵，社会的矛盾",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "【欢迎光临】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "啊？一上来就那么抽象吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "是的 就是那么抽象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "请说请说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "谢谢你的这份热情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "但是我没有你所说的一切问题 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "就不需要了哈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "真的吗我不信",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "【陈鲁豫】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "那你就当我在凡尔赛吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "越解释你越不信了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "我没法向你证明什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "cao  你要这样的话 那我就信了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "【碎了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "全世界只有我在不幸福吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "所以...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "你遇到什么事情了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "该不会以上的所有的问题你都遇到了吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "谢谢您的关心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "倒是也没那么倒霉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "只是普普通通的失业罢了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "现在大环境确实差啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "很多人都在抱怨失业了 找不到工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": " 可以问你是做什么工作的吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "我是幼儿园老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "【叹气】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "那我们也算半个同行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "难道你就是传说中的男幼师吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "没那么稀奇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "我是大学老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "啊？！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "【震惊】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "大学老师不是更稀奇吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "有吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "说某个男生是大学老师的话 大家都觉得是ok的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "如果说是幼师  护士什么的话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "大家才会惊讶吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "我的意思是说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "很厉害",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "hhhh一份工作而已了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "content": "我觉得幼儿园老师也很厉害",
